body:
So when you create your clone, he applies on hit effects, which is exactly what the eye/face is. Its an execute on hit. When you have a clone attack minions you can get bonus gold for yourself and heal the clone with your own executions,since usually the clone will be the closest hero to you. I highly doubt this was intentional, since it makes early tower dives on shaco almost guaranteed (as a support) since you can execute and heal from the minions, while your AD does all of the damage. This is especially a problem late game, because if you have Eye, you have 8 stacks every 50 some seconds that you can use at once for tower dives.

Again, I do not know if this is intentional, but it seems a little bit busted

{{champion:35}}
